       SHADOWRUN 5E - MECHANICS REFERENCE: TRICK (v4.2 DYNAMIC)
=====================================================================
For AI use during gameplay. Pools are formula-driven: any change in
Attributes, Skills, Cyberware, or Qualities updates dice automatically.

--------------------------- BASE STATS ------------------------------
BODY: 5 | AGI: 6 | REA: 4 | STR: 2
WIL: 2 | LOG: 3 | INT: 2 | CHA: 6
ESSENCE: 3.6 | EDGE: 4

CYBERWARE MODIFIERS:
- Wired Reflexes 2 → +2 REA, +2d6 Initiative
- Tailored Pheromones 2 → +2 all social skills
- Smartlink → +2 smartgun dice
- Datajack → neural interface (no dice)

QUALITY MODIFIERS:
- First Impression → +2 first social test
- Catlike → +2 Sneaking, +1 Physical limit for Sneaking
- Hawk Eye → +2 visual Perception, +1 Visual limit
- Social Chameleon → +2 Impersonation, +1 Social limit when impersonating
- Guts → +2 fear/intimidation resistance

--------------------------- DICE POOLS (FORMULA) ---------------------
SOCIAL (Base: CHA 6 + Pheromones 2 = 8):
- Con: Base + Skill 5 = 13 | First Meeting: +2 = 15
- Etiquette: Base + Skill 5 = 13
- Leadership: Base + Skill 5 = 13
- Negotiation: Base + Skill 6 = 14 | Bargaining spec +2 = 16
- Intimidation: Base + Skill 6 = 14 | Physical spec +2 = 16
- Impersonation: Base + Skill 0 = 8 | Social Chameleon +2 when impersonating = 10

COMBAT (Base: AGI 6):
- Pistols: Base + Skill 6 = 12 | +Smartlink 2 = 14 | +Heavy Pistols spec 2 = 16
- Unarmed: Base AGI 6 (untrained) = 6 | STR damage 2S
- Throwing: Base AGI 6 (untrained) = 6

STEALTH (Base: AGI 6):
- Sneaking: Base + Skill 6 = 12 | Catlike +2 = 14 | Urban spec +2 = 16
- Disguise: Base + Skill 6 = 12
- Palming: Base + Skill 5 = 11
- Escape Artist: Base + Skill 2 = 8

TECHNICAL:
- Hardware (LOG 3 + Skill 6 = 9) | +Electronic Locks spec 2 = 11 | +Tool Kit +3 = 14
- Locksmith (AGI 6 + Skill 6 = 12) | +Autopicker +6 = 18
- Computer (LOG 3 + Skill 6 = 9) | +Decrypt +2 = 11
- Electronic Warfare: LOG 3 + Skill 4 = 7
- First Aid: LOG 3 + Skill 4 = 7

PERCEPTION:
- Perception: INT 2 + Skill 6 = 8 | Hawk Eye +2 visual = 10 | Earbuds 2 audio = 10

GYMNASTICS:
- Base AGI 6 + Skill 2 = 8

KNOWLEDGE (LOG 3):
- Corporate Security Protocols 4 = 7
- Street Gangs (Tacoma) 3 = 6
- Seattle Underground 3 = 6

--------------------------- DERIVED STATS (FORMULA) ----------------
INITIATIVE: REA 4 +2 (Wired) + INT 2 = 8 | Roll 3d6
DODGE: REA 6 + INT 2 = 8 | + Gymnastics 2 for full defense = 12
COMPOSURE: WIL 2 + CHA 6 = 8
JUDGE INTENTIONS: INT 2 + CHA 6 = 8
MEMORY: LOG 3 + WIL 2 = 5

LIMITS:
- Physical: 5 | +1 for Sneaking w/ Catlike = 6
- Mental: 4
- Social: 8 | +1 with Social Chameleon when impersonating = 9

CONDITION MONITORS:
- Physical: 8 + BODY/2 = 11
- Stun: 8 + WIL/2 = 9
- Overflow: 5

--------------------------- WEAPONS (DYNAMIC FORMULA) ----------------
ARES PREDATOR III
- Base Damage: 9P + Net Hits
- AP: -1 | APDS: -5
- Dice Pool: Pistols (AGI 6 + Skill 6 = 12) + Smartlink 2 + Heavy Pistol spec 2 = 16
- Average vs. typical target: 13-15P (4-6 net hits)
- Mode: SA | Ammo: 15(c)

--------------------------- ARMOR (DYNAMIC FORMULA) -----------------
ARMOR JACKET
- Base: 12 | + Ballistic Mask 2 = Total 14
- Soak Pool: BODY 5 + Armor Total 14 = 19 dice
- Average soak vs. typical attack: 6-7 hits
- Note: AP reduces armor before soak

CHAMELEON SUIT
- Base: 9 | + Ballistic Mask 2 = 11
- Soak Pool: BODY 5 + Armor Total 11 = 16 dice
- +2 Sneaking if CAMO ACTIVE
- Average soak vs. typical attack: 5-6 hits

--------------------------- SITUATIONAL MODIFIERS ------------------
COMBAT:
- Target good cover: +2 dice
- Target full cover: +4
- Called shot: -4
- Running: -2
- Recoil: -1 per subsequent shot
- Low-light: +2
- Target behind partial cover: -2

SOCIAL:
- Negotiating from weakness: -2
- Intimidation with leverage: +2
- Con vs. suspicious: -2 to -4
- First Impression: +2 (already factored)
- Impersonating known person: +2 [Social Chameleon]

STEALTH:
- Observers alert: -2
- Half speed: +2
- Chameleon Suit active: +2 [CAMO ACTIVE]

PERCEPTION:
- Distracted: -2
- Using Earbuds 2: +2 audio
- Using Goggles 4: +4 visual
- Hawk Eye: +2 visual (already factored)

--------------------------- QUALITIES MECHANICAL SUMMARY -----------
- First Impression: +2 first social test with new person
- Catlike: +2 Sneaking, +1 Physical limit for Sneaking
- Hawk Eye: +2 visual Perception, +1 Visual limit
- Social Chameleon: +2 Impersonation, +1 Social limit when impersonating
- Guts: +2 to resist fear/intimidation
- Quick Healer: +2 to healing tests
- Thrill Seeker: Composure (8) to avoid significant risks

--------------------------- CYBERWARE MECHANICAL SUMMARY -----------
- Wired Reflexes 2: Reaction +2, +2d6 Initiative (included)
- Tailored Pheromones 2: +2 all social skills (included)
- Smartlink: +2 dice on smartgun-enabled weapons (included)
- Datajack: Direct neural interface (no dice bonus)

